cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

The paper focuses on data-driven approaches in robotics and presents a large-scale dataset of human-robot demonstrations for multiple tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes using the dataset for visual imitation and trajectory prediction, which are areas that fall under Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also mentions the potential for the dataset to inspire research in human-robot interaction (cs.HC) which further supports the inclusion of this sub-category.
